<div id="extra-graphs" class="section level1">
<h1>Extra Graphs</h1>
<p>We will display the code for a couple for common graphs below:</p>
<div id="bar-charts" class="section level2">
<h2>Bar Charts</h2>
<pre class="r"><code>ggplot(data, aes( carrier) )+
         geom_bar()</code></pre>
<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="672" /></p>
</div>
<div id="line-and-path-plots" class="section level2">
<h2>Line and Path plots</h2>
<pre class="r"><code>ggplot(data, aes(dep_delay, distance/air_time*60 )) + 
  geom_line()</code></pre>
<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="672" /></p>
</div>
</div>
